Revision history for RT::Extension::HistoryFilter

3.01 2021-01-17
 - Generate pot file for further translations
 - Add french translation
 - update Module::Install for RT 5.0 compatibility

2.03 2018-09-30
 - Fix affecting on Assets, User, Groups history page
 - update Module::Install and friends

2.02 2018-02-05
 - update Module::Install and friends
 - add a hint to this extension on the configuration widget
 - sync html/Widgets/Form/Select with RT 4.4.2
 - filter transactions on all pages except ticket history
 - add .travis.yml
 - add some basic tests
 - update Module::Install::RTx

2.01 2016-05-30
 - update Module::Install::ReadmeFromPod
 - support SelfService again

2.00 2016-02-25
 - use the same callback for all supported RT version
 - RT 4.4 compatibility

1.01 2014-08-26
 - update select widget
 - get transaction types from BriefDescriptions hash instead of a static list

1.00 2013-10-22
 - update select widget
 - RT 4.2 compatibility

0.03 2011-05-20
 - RT 4.0 compatibility

0.02 2010-06-13
 - First version released to CPAN
 - update MANIFEST and MANIFEST.SKIP

0.01 2010-05-31
 - initial release
